ogical sort to determine execution order\n- Circular dependencies throw error: `\"Circular dependency detected: {name}\"`\n- Missing dependencies throw error: `\"Missing dependency: {name} requires {dep}\"`\n\n#### **Plugin Factory Pattern**\nAll plugins export a factory function:\n```typescript\nexport function createXxxPlugin(): Plugin {\n  return {\n    name: 'xxx',\n    version: '1.0.0',\n    dependencies: [],\n    hooks: {\n      // implement hooks as needed\n    }\n  };\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n### 7. KEY TYPES AND INTERFACES SUMMARY\n\n| Type | Purpose | Key Fields |\n|------|---------|-----------|\n| `SiteConfig` | Site metadata | title, baseUrl, outputDir, contentDir, templateDir |\n| `ContentFile` | Individual content | slug, title, content, metadata, date?, tags?, template? |\n| `BuildContext` | Build state | config, files, output, assets, data |\n| `Plugin` | Plugin definition | name, version, dependencies, hooks |\n| `PluginHooks` | Plugin entry points | beforeBuild?, transformContent?, afterBuild? |\n| `Template` | Template renderer | name, render function |\n\n---\n\n### 8. COMPLETE DIRECTORY TREE\n\n```\n/workspace/\n├── .eslintrc.cjs\n├── .gitignore\n├── .thunderdome/\n│   └── rubric.yaml\n├── package.json\n├── package-lock.json\n├── tsconfig.json\n├── vitest.config.ts\n├── TASK.md\n├── src/\n│   ├── core/\n│   │   ├── types.ts           (44 lines - 6 interfaces)\n│   │   ├── engine.ts          (117 lines - BuildEngine class)\n│   │   ├── templates.ts       (43 lines - 2 template factories)\n│   │   └── index.ts           (4 lines - exports)\n│   └── plugins/\n│       └── .gitkeep\n└── tests/\n    ├── core.test.ts           (195 lines - 15 tests)\n    └── plugins/\n        ├── asset-pipeline.test.ts      (107 lines - 8 tests)\n        ├── dev-server.test.ts          (95 lines - 8 tests)\n        ├── markdown-ext.test.ts        (90 lines - 8 tests)\n        ├── rss-feed.test.ts            (120 lines - 7 tests)\n        ├── search-index.test.ts        (114 l